ve power of business in solving global problems and to reframe sustainabili=
ty as an opportunity rather than a responsibility. The B Team=E2=80=99s rec=
ent work focuses on promoting an inclusive stakeholder approach, which Zeit=
z is implementing at Harley-Davidson, as he did at Puma. While he acknowled=
ged that large-scale transformation is a long-term process, he said: =
=E2=80=9CI=E2=80=99m a realistic optimist. =E2=80=A6 We=E2=80=99re starting=
 to realize what the problems are and starting to find solutions. I remain =
