=09The formula for comedy :: =
Comedy has a formula: tragedy plus time, said Noah. =E2=80=9CAs long as you=
 have enough time that separates you enough from the tragedy, no matter how=
 small or big it is, you=E2=80=99ll be able to laugh at it. The issue is ri=
