=09The war for attention :=
: Every platform is fighting a war for users=E2=80=99 attention. =E2=80=
=9CIf Netflix gets me to binge-watch three times 10 episodes of Narcos, whi=
ch I did,=E2=80=9D he said, =E2=80=9Cthat=E2=80=99s 30 hours that music doe=
sn=E2=80=99t see, that Facebook or Instagram doesn=E2=80=99t see.=E2=80=
=9D Netflix has won the attention war for 30 hours. Page believes that comp=
